      <subfield code="a">Introduction -- Working together to create value for customers -- Sales and marketing don't always get along -- Taking a look under the hood of the interface -- Mending the rift between sales and marketing -- Assessing your sales-marketing interface -- Challenges to your sales-marketing interface.</subfield>
